sections.heading: of courts of record other than district courts; duties
sections.text: The provisions of sections 25-2204 to 25-2211 shall, as far as applicable, apply to clerks of other courts of record.SourceR.S.1867, Code § 888, p. 548;R.S.1913, § 8562;C.S.1922, § 9513;C.S.1929, § 20-2214;R.S.1943, § 25-2213;Laws 1992, LB 1059,
